  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In RealityKit, cameras define the point of view from which RealityKit renders a scene."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In AR mode, RealityKit creates and controls the camera for you based on the location and orientation of the device."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In non-AR mode, you can control the camera by adding an entity that holds one of the camera components"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "below and changing its "
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/Transform",
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Lighting and shadows are an essential part of creating immersive and realistic experiences."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can craft dynamic and visually appealing environments that respond naturally"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "to the viewer’s movement and other actions by strategically placing and configuring lights and cameras."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
